						               													<description>Got a scenario you're dying to try out, but don't want to learn pages of complicated rules?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New to gaming and ready to get your feet wet?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Experienced gamer looking for simple rules with a unique approach?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;QUIK FRIK is a one-page rule set (with a bonus page) that offers a unique approach to miniatures skirmish gaming, for scenarios from WWII through sci-fi. These rules emphasize the friction that can mount during combat. They are well suited for small-scale combat, from a handful of figures up to a platoon. They are best for 6-20mm miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules are included for movement and combat, including vehicles. Combat results can be seen with just one roll of the dice on one combat table. A unique activation sequence is also featured. Forces can be regular or elite, and the bonus page offers many special abilities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With QUIK FRIK, your favorite scenario can be as mindblowing as your favorite movie scene, and it can go almost as fast. So get your game on right now.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
